  }, "Lola Hunt:")), mdx("p", null, "Yeah, so, child sexual abuse material is something that exists. I just want to point out, like acknowledge that it's not something that we're for obviously, it is something that does exist. However, a lot of the organizations that are currently fighting it, their main aim isn't really to get rid of child sex or sexual abuse material. Because the approaches that they are taking don't actually prevents that material from being produced in the first place."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
